## External Monitoring (Recommended)

For true 24/7 uptime, use an external service:

### UptimeRobot Setup
1. Go to uptimerobot.com
2. Add New Monitor
3. Monitor Type: HTTP(s)
4. Friendly Name: Polling System Keep-Alive
5. URL: `https://your-backend-url.onrender.com/health`
6. Monitoring Interval: 5 minutes
7. Save

This ensures your server stays active even when no users are online.
